{"tid":2246401,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做左10年野返工心態","createTime":"2020-10-17T04:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T04:55:35.000Z","uid":102081,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c91171940aeec798e929d1b9f29b718fad168eb9","tid":2246401,"uid":102081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"人生到左32，做個小小經理仔<br />\n<br />\n以前返工好想好快完成晒所有野，自己落手落腳做，為求快靚正，好想學好多野，好有野心咁，不計較咁做同做到OT。<br />\n<br />\n宜家就變到好似得過且過，但求生活快樂就好，d job 推得就推，拖得就拖。做一件事時，都係慢慢plan完再諗下再慢慢做野，吾想做落手落腳做，心態上想過得一日得一日，返工都係等出糧同收工，對新事物學習好似興趣不太大咁。<br />\n<br />\n有無人都係咁？"},{"pid":"46679ce1cb233eb34db0b611b93ee6f94d6e242e","tid":2246401,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:43:48.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"83123c25e3ad6a1bec771b801ccb6ba6dc387b37","tid":2246401,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"46679ce1cb233eb34db0b611b93ee6f94d6e242e","tid":2246401,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:43:48.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:44:43.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"fbeab1a566b9a3297d5ec6b5fbd9d1fc5f6323d8","tid":2246401,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:47:01.000Z","msg":"打份工咁快有咩用"},{"pid":"3157b493b2891a98c140c050ffa09fb453465b8f","tid":2246401,"uid":312363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83123c25e3ad6a1bec771b801ccb6ba6dc387b37","tid":2246401,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"46679ce1cb233eb34db0b611b93ee6f94d6e242e","tid":2246401,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:43:48.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:44:43.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T04:47:51.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"ae00d8acf5d02489dfba7b614913a41c0ad25421","tid":2246401,"uid":102081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbeab1a566b9a3297d5ec6b5fbd9d1fc5f6323d8","ti